summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Seventh Avenue North from Prospect Street, to the north line of Union Lake Supplemental Addition in the City of Seattle, by constructing concrete sidewalks under Ordinance No. 18407, creating Local Improvement District No. 1736 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
